{"tid":2285692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英擬再售台北物業套現 地產中介稱未有買家","createTime":"2020-11-14T10:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T17:37:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51238cda70f7fe54c743fdff2ccc88d73f9c6fa5","tid":2285692,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wsSZ2W7Ax0PMVHLa4VIf0Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/c4b043a6ff376929bf64799365df12de\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwsSZ2W7Ax0PMVHLa4VIf0Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fc4b043a6ff376929bf64799365df12de&h=9d25fa46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=26fa6384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】不斷蝕錢的壹傳媒黎智英近年頻頻出售在台灣的物業套現，近年他將《台灣蘋果日報》位於台北市內湖區總部的4幢辦公大樓出售，只留下一幢自用。據台媒周五（13日）報道，該幢僅餘的大樓近日出現在網絡房屋租售平台。有地產中介透露，該大樓被委託銷售的消息已傳出多時，但至今未有合適的買方出現。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，黎智英在內湖區原本持有5幢辦公大樓。2018年，他將A、B兩幢《台灣蘋果日報》大樓以近18億元（新台幣，下同，約5億港元）出售予台灣人壽。去年，他再將D幢台灣壹電視大樓和E幢壹同樂動畫大樓，分別售予中國電器和敏恩國際，分別作價14.5億元（約4億港元）和9.1億元（約2.5億港元）。近期在網路房屋租售平台《窩牛網》，出現C幢原台灣《壹週刊》大樓的出售訊息，但未標明售價。<br />\n<br />\n除內湖區物業外，黎智英去年以3.1億元（約8,600萬港元），將高雄岡山區的一幅地皮連印刷廠物業售予台灣大鎪科技。台灣上市建築商長虹建設於2013和2019年，分別向黎智英及其相關公司購入位於內湖區和新北市土城區共3幅地皮，涉額逾100億元（約27.6億港元）。據統計，黎智英及其公司自2013年以來單是出售商廈、廠房及地皮，總交易金額超過145億元（約40億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，官司纏身的黎智英，早前涉嫌違反《港區國安法》而被拘捕扣查40小時後獲准保釋，期間已傳出他繼續出售資產套現，有指包括由黎牽頭持有的大埔太平工業中心一個超過4萬方呎全層物業，委託代理放售，更劈逾兩成至約1.29億元，可見他去貨套現心切。<br />\n<br />\n而在黎智英被捕前不久，曾在壹傳媒旗下《壹週刊》節目內直言，不論是否移民，首要做的是要把資產移到海外，並要增加資產的流動性，別待要走時才慢慢變賣。而2018年至今，黎在台灣已不斷賣產，當中包括台北內湖區壹電視大樓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JpSLkb6wg7plC0SP1M9y2g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/ba3d9382953f6d4ac78a16000893218d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJpSLkb6wg7plC0SP1M9y2g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fba3d9382953f6d4ac78a16000893218d&h=0f09a340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vC2Ip8IYUX3FRBQ24uaqrA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/eb83130000e8a41dadec82992cf2b608\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvC2Ip8IYUX3FRBQ24uaqrA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Feb83130000e8a41dadec82992cf2b608&h=dbdea255&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f03dbdb4853d710675388c6358d5c959872c9b08","tid":2285692,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"蘋果已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1abe2e75bb9d8feaa95f72328a6e66bf361bf3a","tid":2285692,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03dbdb4853d710675388c6358d5c959872c9b08","tid":2285692,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"蘋果已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f848514be8e9